name: Bitcoin Pizza 79921
description: This NFT entitles the owner to claim the Bitcoin Pizza #79921 (InscriptionID: 92b48e1533f1fe172bf7b7b3041633fdabcbbbeef931dca5ab92d539b7530174i0) inscribed on the Bitcoin Blockchain. Ordinals are digital assets inscribed on Satoshis, the lowest denomination of Bitcoin (BTC). Please open a Support Ticket in our Discord to Claim the Pizza. In order to claim the Ordinal, a compatible Bitcoin address is required. Please follow this Tutorial to Setup a compatible Bitcoin Wallet: https://docs.raredough.com/receiving-bitcoin-ordinals
